INSTALLATION: Install.
              Use keygen to generate your "Site License" serial.

       NOTES: 
              The name function in the keygen has the only purpose
              to make your serial unique to you. You can still register
              URL Helper with any name with the generated key.
              Please use chars like a-z and/or numbers. Chars like %_# )]/!
              will work but might be banned in future versions.
              
              Nuff said. Enjoy! / ONY

       ABOUT:

              URL Helper, the best and easy to use url sniffer (url snooper).

              To download windows media streaming, realmedia streaming, flash video
              and other streaming, you need to know the url(the file name and
              server address) of you want to download.

              Unfortunately, some links to streaming audio and video that you come
              across on the web are hidden behind javascript or activex scripts.
              Because of this, it is sometimes very difficult to figure out the
              actual urls that correspond to the streams being played.

              URL Helper provide a one-step solution to finding the URLs for all 
              streams. It does this by searching files and watching network traffic
              and identifying  potential urls

              Key Features:

              * One-step solution to find the URLs
              * Capture RealMedia,Windows Media, flash streaming video and
                other streams.
              * Saveother website&#039;s flash video.
              * Build-in simply downloader
              * Download automatically those files which you want to save them
                into  your PC
              * Support proxy server
              * Multi-Language
              
              blah, blah, blah...
